@database ShAsk
@node main ShAsk

                  @{b}ShAsk, a replacement of the Ask CLI command
                  -------------------------------------------@{ub}

ShAsk is a command executable that is the result of a condition that
followed the feeling I had that I'd like to write some code but didn't
really want to continue working on any of my bigger projects. So I had
the idea of a program that would prompt the user for a Yes or No answer
using an Intuition requester.

         @{" Command specification                " link ShAsk_1}
         @{" Registration                         " link ShAsk_2}
         @{" Contact addresses                    " link ShAsk_3}
         @{" Version history                      " link ShAsk_4}

