@node ShAsk_4
@title "Version history"
@{b}Version history@{ub}

V1.00    22.11.   First version. Operates exactly similar to original Ask.

V2.00    23.11.   Now prompts using an Intuition requester! Really COOL.

V3.00    23.11.   Use of timer added. Now returns Yes if user doesn't
                  answer in four seconds.

V3.10    23.11.   This version adds command line arguments TIMEOUT and
                  DEFAULT. These control the way the requester acts.
                  By default timeout feature is off and default is Yes.

V3.11    24.11.   A minor update with an unnecessary function call
                  removed and a nonvolatile meaningless bug fixed.
                  This is the final version for now, and the version
                  of the executable provided in this package.
@endnode

